thread.title: Reality TV show TOWIE returns tonight and Devon models set to debut

author: Alex Richards
title: Reality TV show TOWIE returns tonight and Devon models set to debut
text:
What's On Reality TV show TOWIE returns tonight and Devon models set to debut The Only Way is Essex is back for its 22nd series - with a bullied schoolgirl from Derriford on the cast list Share Alex Richards Deputy News Editor 20:28, 25 MAR 2018   Thank you for subscribing!   
Reality TV hit The Only Way is Essex returns tonight and - despite its Brentwood setting - is expected to feature two glamour models from Devon. 
Glamorous Shelby Tribble is among the new faces in this year's 2018 cast. And, Clelia Theodorou, also from Plymouth, could be appearing too. Read More Who is Shelby? Shelby Tribble 
Plymouth Herald revealed that Shelby Tribble, the former Miss Great Britain, was born and raised in Devon and made her name in Derriford before moving to London. 
Aged 15 Shelby joined Plymouth Diving - on the same day as Tom Daley - and she pursued her interest in the sport for two years, travelling to compete in competitions. 
In her short career, Shelby has won a series of beauty pageants, including Miss South West, Miss Hippodrome 2014, Miss Loaded 2014 and has been a Miss England finalist. Who is Clelia? 
Clelia Theodorou, has modelled for brands such as Rebellious Fashion and Luxe To Kill. 
An insider told The Sun that Clelia is going to shake things up on the show and will "throw the cast into chaos." 
It’s been widely rumoured that Theodorou is dating TOWIE Dan Edgar, Mirror Online claim. Read More Katie Hopkins and Exeter MP Ben Bradshaw in Twitter spat over Brexit marches 
It’s caused quite a stir, with Edgar’s ex-girlfriend Amber Turner, another TOWIE cast member, reportedly been left feeling "mugged off". 
The 25-year-old TOWIE star was left crushed last year when she struck up a casual romance with the Essex lad but discovered Dan had slept with Theodorou. 
And the blonde beauty "can't stop crying" since finding out the news just 48 hours after they started filming in Barcelona. When is TOWIE on and what channel is it on? 
The Only Way Is Essex will be on at 9pm on Sundays on ITVbe. 
The first programme airs tonight - Sunday, March 25. Like us on Facebook
